metadata.name: Circle of Zav #1
metadata.description: The CoZ NFT is your access pass to all. Flagship utility will be access to claims of future art releases exclusively done by Zav. Side-lined Utility will be purely fueled by the community and will head into the designated trajectory demanded by the Circle, This can consist of anything from quality private alpha to workshops with real meaningful skillful benefits with free access to members of the circle accompanied with fulfilling the community's wishes for a more unique yet favorable out of the ordinary execution style.
